quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  34,40,"√Ďande o moo…ďtindiroyta …ďe dendaangal, refti o daalana Maleykaaji …ďin: "E ko …ďee …óoo (yim…ďe) ndewatnoo on?""
  34,41,"∆Āe mbi'a: "Senayee woodanii ma! Ko Aan woni gi…óo amen ga ma…ď…ďe. Toode ko jinnaaji …óin …ďe ndewaynoo, ko …ďuri …óuu…óude e ma…ď…ďe, ko …óin (jinnaaji) gooŇč…óini"."
  34,42,"Hannde non, yoga mon waawanaa yoga nafa wanaa lorra. Min mbi'anoya …ďen too√Ī…ďe: "Mee…óee lepte Yiite nge pennatno…óon fii mum"."
  34,43,"Si aayeeje amen …ďanngu…óe …óen janngaamma e ma…ď…ďe, …ďe mbi'a: "oo wonaani, si wonaa gorko paalaa…óo palagol on e ko baabiraa…ďe mon ndewayno rewaynoo". ∆Āe mbi'i: "Ndee (Alqur‚Äôaanaare) wonaani, si wonaa fenaande fekindaande". Yeddu…ďe …ďen mb'ani goonga kan nde ka arnoo e ma…ď…ďe: "Ndee wonaani, si wanaa mbilewu …ďanngu ngu"."
  34,44,"Min ngaddanaani …ďee, defte …óe …ďe janngata. Min mee…óaani nulude e ma…ď…ďe, jeertinoowo ado maa."
  34,45,"Adinoo…ďe …ďe …ďen [kadi] njenniino (nulaa…ďe mum). [Yim…ďe maa …ďen] njottaaki sappa…ďal ko Min ngkkunoo …ďen kon. ∆Āen njeddi Nulaa…ďe Amen …ďen, taskii no lepte am …óen mba'unoo!"
  34,46,"Maaku: "nganndee ko mi waajorta on, ko (hu'unde) wootere: "Ko nde daroranton Alla …ói…óo …ói…óo e gooto gooto, refti miijito…óon. (Nganndon) wondii…óo mon on aldaa e jinna: O wonaani, si wonaa jerrtinoowo on, e ko woni yeeso (mon), e lepte ca…ótu…óe"."
  34,47,"Maaku: "Mi la…ďndaaki on njo…ďdi, …óuum ko fii mon. Njo…ďdi am ndin wonaani, si wonaa ka Alla. KaŇčko Ko o Seedii…óo e kala hu'unde"."
  34,48,"Maaku: "pellet, Joomi am ko nerlortoo…óo [meere nden, hujjaaji] goonga ka, timmin…óo anndugol wirnii…ói"."